page.title: 14THE BEEF-EATER HIGH WYCOMBE
page.content: The Beef-eater is a{restaurant}.It is fifty years old and was a pub when it was built.It has been a "Steak-house" for just over a year.The{menu}consists of a piece of beef,or fish with chips served with salad.You can have wine with the meal.One thing you may do is fill in a form saying when your child's birthday is then take him or her to the "steak-house"as a birthday treat.There will be a birthday party waiting.The{life-style}of a lot of people is to eat away from home at the Beef-eater on one day of the week, usually at the weekend.
